metadata.name: it is not difficult to say,
metadata.description:
something that everyone has.



The learning talent of Wang Xian is still the same as the previous life, it is the most common talent. The effect is that after using the skill, you will gain a certain amount of proficiency, which is only about 1% bonus.



But it doesn't matter anymore.



Wang Xian looked at the dragon and phoenix jade pendant in his hand. The information about the jade pendant appeared in front of his eyes.



Bad jade: Worthless, but there seems to be something inside. You should probably try to break the jade.
